## Troubleshooting

### "Tool not found"

**Cause**: Tool name doesn't match available tools

**Solution**: Ask AI to list available tools first

### "Invalid parameters"

**Cause**: Required parameters missing or wrong type

**Solution**: Check tool description for parameter requirements

### "Operation failed"

**Cause**: Tool execution encountered an error

**Solution**: Check error message for details, verify prerequisites

